fulfill its commitments and curb terrorist activities.
</P>
<P>
Netanyahu made the appeal after the right-wing in his
government asked him to take measures to deal with the terrorist
threats. (BC-Israel-Palestine-Terror)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
BAGHDAD -- Oil production and export systems in Iraq are in
critical conditions due to the delayed arrival of spare parts and
production requirements for oil installations, said an Iraqi Oil
Ministry source.
</P>
<P>
In a statement carried by the Iraqi News Agency on Sunday, the
unnamed source said without spare parts, it is hard for Iraq to
repair any accidental failure now.
</P>
<P>
So far Iraq has signed 111 contracts valued at 100 million
U.S. dollars to purchase oil spare parts, but the U.N. Sanctions
Committee has approved only seven and put on hold five others,
said the source. (BC-Iraq-Oil-Spare Parts)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
