<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, August 31 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar started
the local trading week on a fresh and more optimistic note Monday,
maintaining the gains seen offshore during the weekend.
</P>
