<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 31 (Xinhua) -- Vice-chairman of the Central
Military Commission and State Councillor Chi Haotian held
friendly talks here today with visiting New Zealand Defense
Minister Max Bradford.
</P>
<P>
Chi, who is also Chinese defense minister, had an extensive and
in-depth exchange of views with his New Zealand guests on
bilateral ties, the Asia-Pacific region situation, and other
issues of common concern.
</P>
<P>
